to claim you're dating Preaw?

3
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,400
{\an8}Why can't I?

4
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:17,480
{\an8}Even we have slept together too.

5
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:24,640
{\an8}You're just a coward
who won't admit the truth!

6
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,520
{\an8}You just like Mook better than me.

7
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:31,200
{\an8}- Feed him! Feed him!
- Feed him! Feed him!

8
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:35,760
{\an8}- Feed him! Feed him!
- Feed him! Yay

9
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:40,560
Mom said she was going to buy us food.

10
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:46,600
But… But she never came back.

11
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:49,920
Tawan, my brother, he's dead.

12
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,160
There, there.

13
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,320
Don't cry.

14
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,840
It's alright, sweetie. Don't cry.

15
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:02,000
Teacher, what should we do?

16
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,080
Can you help him in any way?

17
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,680
I'd better take him to the police,

18
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,520
in case anyone's reported
the kids as missing.

19
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,560
It's okay.

20
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:12,960
Don't be scared, sweetie.

21
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,920
Don't cry. You're with her now.

22
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:18,360
Don't be scared, okay? Stay with me here.

23
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:21,560
I'll help you find your mom,
alright, sweetie?

24
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,680
- Did you just get back from a flight?
- Yeah.

25
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,960
Are you okay?

26
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:45,760
Early morning flights
always make me so tired.

27
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:54,360
Does Preaw not have many shifts lately?

28
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,440
How come I rarely see her?

29
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:03,800
Remember the boyfriend
she revealed at the party?

30
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:09,360
I heard he's abusive,

31
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,480
and Preaw got beaten.

32
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,079
That Top guy?

33
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,040
He's that horrible?

34
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:25,200
