35
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:28,240
because our flight schedule's
been pretty weird lately,

36
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,600
so I don't know if it's true or not.

37
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,640
Why are you at my house?

38
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,120
What's the matter, Khim?

39
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,800
Can you open the gate for me?

40
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:06,040
Amp told me you haven't shown up
to work for a while now.

41
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,080
Are you okay?

42
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:12,680
No, no. I'm fine. I'm just…

43
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:16,840
a little sick, so I asked
for a schedule change.

44
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,760
If there's nothing else,

45
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,680
I'll be going back to rest now.

46
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,000
Hey.

47
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,800
- Thank you.
- Careful.

48
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,680
Smells so good.

49
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:43,000
I was just craving coffee, Boss.

50
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:46,440
So you're done with shooting
for the couple campaign?

51
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,600
Don't tease me, Boss.

52
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,880
