I have to keep pretending.

53
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,400
There's news to consume daily these days.

54
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,880
Once a new trend comes, it will die down.

55
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:04,400
What I'm more worried about

56
