59
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,720
Here.

60
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:20,280
I'm almost done
with the packages' pricing table.

61
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:23,360
We should promote it along
with Mr. Thee's wedding campaign.

62
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:27,080
I want to pump out
lots of online promotions in this period.

63
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,720
Yeah.

64
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:32,840
Mook, don't work so hard that you forget

65
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,160
about our kids' showcase at school today.

66
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,000
Oh, right.

67
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:39,280
I'll hurry and finish my work.

68
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:41,200
