69
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,600
- Sure.
- Okay.

70
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,600
Mook!

71
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:51,240
Mook, many pages are posting
bad reviews of our company.

72
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:57,000
