made a post slandering our tours.

73
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,120
So many pages did.

74
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:04,480
<i>Their trips suck.</i>
<i>The hotel doesn't match the photos.</i>

75
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:07,120
<i>Terrible service. Expensive too.</i>

76
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,360
{\an8}<i>No cancellations, they say.</i>

77
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:11,360
{\an8}<i>Well, I'm cancelling them myself.</i>

78
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:13,080
<i>I'm so done.</i>

79
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:16,240
<i>I'll give you a hint.</i>
<i>It's called "A Round" something.</i>

80
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:28,800
Could it be someone
trying to sabotage our company?

81
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,640
Excuse me.

82
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:41,640
The van rentals that used
to work with us just called.

83
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:44,360
So many of them cancelled our bookings.

84
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,840
But why?

85
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,960
Mook,

86
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,320
I think we can deal with this
in a meeting tomorrow.

87
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:56,960
Right now, we have to go,
or we'll be late for school.

88
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:58,720
Let's go.

89
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:02,440
Boss, can I leave Kongkwan in your care?

90
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,720
I want to solve these problems first.

91
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:07,360
Are you sure, Mook?

92
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:11,600
Kongkwan will be sad
if her mom doesn't go see her work.

93
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:16,000
It's alright. I'll explain to her
when I pick her up.

94
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:20,120
Then, call me if you need anything.

95
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,360
I'll take care of the kids.

96
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,760
Thank you, Boss.

97
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,360
- See you later.
- See you later.

98
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,520
- Yes.
- Okay.

99
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,600
- See you later, Boss.
- Yes.

100
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,760
Right.

101
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:32,640
Can I have the numbers
of the van rentals that cancelled on us?

102
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,919
I'll call them.

103
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,799
I'll make a list and text it to you.

104
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,400
Yes.

105
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:43,799
I'm sure someone's trying to sabotage us
by damaging our reputation.

106
