107
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:57,840
<i>Remember the boyfriend</i>
<i>she revealed at the party?</i>

108
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,440
<i>I heard he's abusive,</i>

109
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,080
<i>and Preaw got beaten.</i>

110
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:06,280
Why are you at my house?
What's the matter, Khim?

111
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,960
Can you open the gate for me?

112
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,800
<i>Did Ploy not tell you two?</i>

113
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:16,400
She moved out with Top.

114
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,800
We haven't talked since the wedding.

115
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,920
Where did they move to?

116
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:32,280
I just can't seem
to get hold of her lately.

117
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,320
She's at Top's condo.

118
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:37,360
She said she's been tied up
with work lately.

119
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,960
She hasn't been home for many days.

120
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:43,920
It's normal for newly-wed couples.

121
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,120
Top probably can't stay
too far away from her.

122
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:50,600
It's good, though. It means
I'll have a grandkid very soon.

123
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:56,560
So, do you know where his condo is?

124
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:58,840
Actually, Ploy did tell me,

125
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,600
but I can't remember.

126
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:03,800
Can you try calling her again?

127
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,120
Of course.

128
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,480
Oh, Ploy!

129
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,600
Hello?

130
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:38,400
<i>I sent you something. Please read it.</i>

131
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,400
Hey, Top!

132
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:17,640
{\an8}I really appreciate it, Mr. Chit.

133
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:22,240
I'll send my company's
entire van rental schedule to you.

134
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,360
We'll pay more than A Round Trip,

135
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,680
