137
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:34,160
Yes, thank you so much, Mr. Chit.

138
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,240
Goodbye.

139
00:11:37,800 --> 00:11:39,920
Usa, are you sure

140
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:43,000
