145
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,840
What if Mr. Thee looks into this?

146
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,760
Will he find out we did this?

147
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:07,600
Kuk, there are so many
internet trolls these days.

148
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:09,920
How could they ever track one down?

149
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:13,880
These days, this is the way
to survive in business.

150
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,640
Just trust me.

151
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,640
You'll get the big project soon.

152
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,240
My mom told me

153
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,680
