154
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:32,800
Thank you.

155
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:43,080
Coming up next is Kongkwan's work.

156
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:01,480
Kongkwan, you can start now.

157
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:04,760
I love Mommy a lot.

158
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,840
She loves me a lot too.

159
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:09,760
Mommy is like my angel.

160
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,120
Thank you.

161
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,160
