to see her kid's work.

162
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,680
Poor girl.

163
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:22,680
Yeah.

164
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,680
Coming up next is Poonpun's work.

165
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:31,440
<i>How could you do this, Mr. Chit?</i>

166
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:35,040
We've worked together many years,
and we've always kept you busy.

167
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:38,280
