178
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:13,280
If it's not too different, we'll be okay.

179
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:17,520
Okay. I'll find a new supplier
and have them send us a quotation.

180
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,800
- Sure.
- Okay.

181
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,360
Whan?

182
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:23,840
Can you look into the accounts
that gave us bad reviews?

183
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,320
I want to know who's behind it.

184
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,240
Sure.

185
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,760
Come on in.

186
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:45,480
What's up?

187
00:14:55,280 --> 00:14:56,760
Kongkwan.

188
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:59,800
Once your mom's done with work,
she'll be right over.

189
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:01,480
Okay, Uncle.

190
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:04,960
She's really busy lately.

191
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:06,440
Please don't be mad at her.

192
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,240
- Excuse me.
- Yes?

193
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:14,200
