194
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,240
Thank you.

195
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:21,400
Kongkwan, I need to take
Poonpun to the dentist.

196
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:23,920
I'll take you for pizza later, okay?

197
00:15:24,800 --> 00:15:25,680
Okay.

198
00:15:26,800 --> 00:15:27,680
See you later.

199
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:29,040
- See you later.
- See you later.

200
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,400
