217
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:30,560
No, you're not. Stay still.

218
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,200
Excuse me.

219
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:44,040
Hello?

220
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:47,800
Sorry, what?

221
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:50,840
Yes, I'll be right over.

222
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,720
What happened, Mook?

223
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:55,120
Kongkwan's gone missing.

224
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,240
Thank you.

225
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:06,920
Good afternoon.

226
