- Kongkwan!

245
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:02,400
Kongkwan, can you hear me?

246
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:03,320
- Mook.
- Honey.

247
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,280
- Mook.
- Kongkwan!

248
